::Ender::
    "I can fly.  I chose a flyer as the specific type of drone for my beast 
mode."  He spreads his insectoid wings.  They glimmer with a rainbow effect.  
The thin membrane appears oily in the sunlight.  "They may look flimsy but 
they aren't."
